  <thing id="raURakBoun" name="Bound to Master" description="A raktavarna is forever bound to the rakshasa who created it. What it sees the rakshasa knows, and this includes anything the raktavarna views via clairaudience/clairvoyance. The range of this bond is unlimited (functioning even across planes). Casting dispel evil on a raktavarna stuns its rakshasa master for 1d4 rounds (no save). A rakshasa can sever the bond at will, though doing so kills the raktavarna instantly." compset="RaceSpec">
