  <thing id="raUContBar" name="Continuous Barrage" description="If a beatific one hits with the last attack of its flurry of blows, it may attempt an additional attack at a &#150;2 penalty. If this attack hits, the beatific one may continue to make additional attacks, with a cumulative &#150;2 penalty for each subsequent attack (&#150;4 for the second attack, &#150;6 for the third, and so on). If any attack misses, the barrage ends." compset="RaceSpec">
