  <thing id="raUAkaUnHa" name="Unhallow" description="An akaruzug emanates a 40-foot aura of unholy energy, as per the spell unhallow. The construct&apos;s creator determines what, if any, additional spell effects are tied to the akaruzug&apos;s unhallow aura at the time of its creation. The construct benefits from any spell effects tied to its unhallow aura. Common choices are darkness, detect good, freedom of movement, and invisibility purge." compset="RaceSpec">
