  <thing id="raUSoulSla" name="Soul Slave" description="Using the soul trapped within its frame, an akaruzug can manifest ghostly representations of its victim to attack its enemies as a standard action. These soul slaves appear as the akaruzug&apos;s victim did in life and wield a weapon favored by that individual. Aside from this, the soul slave functions similarly to the spell spiritual weapon cast by a 15th level cleric (though with an AC adjusted by the victim&apos;s size). An akaruzug can use this ability up to three times a day." compset="RaceSpec">
