  <thing id="raUWrathBS" name="Wrath" description="A bonestorm cuts apart creatures occupying the same space as it, not just with splintered bones and bludgeoning skulls, but with the unholy energies of the damned souls that make up the undead whirlwind. Thus, 2d6 points of the damage dealt by a bone swarm is physical, and 2d6 points are unholy damage, resulting directly from unholy power." compset="RaceSpec">
