  <thing id="raUTeleSav" name="Telepathic Savant" description="A havero can transmit vague impressions of its thoughts across limitless distances to any creature it is aware of. A havero does not communicate using language and its thoughts are limited and often unintelligible to mortal minds. A havero contacting a creature using this ability does not subject the target to its alien mind." compset="RaceSpec">
