    </thing>
  <thing id="raUCrushMo" name="Crush" description="As a standard action, a flying mobogo may land on opponents of Medium size or smaller, using its terrible girth to crush them. A crush attack affects as many creatures as can fit under the mobogo&apos;s body. Creatures in the affected area must succeed on a DC 22 Reflex save or be pinned, automatically taking 2d8+13 bludgeoning damage during the next round unless the mobogo moves off them.\n\nIf the mobogo chooses to maintain the pin, treat it as a normal grapple attack. Pinned opponents take damage from the crush each round if they don&apos;t escape. The save DC is Constitution-based." compset="RaceSpec">
